    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. The powertrain remains exceptionally healthy, featuring recently adjusted valve clearances and a documented VANOS overhaul to ensure peak torque delivery. The chassis has been properly addressed with subframe reinforcement plates, mitigating the platform\u2019s primary weak point. It retains its factory 6-speed manual transmission and limited-slip differential for an engaging, analog experience. While the finish shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical components\u2014including the cooling system and suspension bushings\u2014are dialed in for immediate performance. A mechanically sound icon ready for the backroads.",
      "price": 32500.0,
