    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2017 BMW M3 is a stunning example of precision engineering, finished in a deep Mineral Grey Metallic that catches the light beautifully. The exterior remains sharp, with a high-gloss finish and only minor, expected road peppering on the front fascia consistent with its mileage. Inside, the Sakhir Orange Merino leather interior offers a striking contrast, showing minimal bolster wear and a pristine dashboard free of any sun damage or cracks. Mechanically, this vehicle has been fastidiously maintained with a complete service log; the twin-turbo inline-six pulls strongly, and the dual-clutch transmission shifts with crisp, immediate response. All electronics, from the head-up display to the premium Harman Kardon sound system, function perfectly. It sits on original 19-inch 437M wheels wrapped in Michelin Pilot Sport tires with plenty of life remaining. This is a smoke-free, garage-kept car that delivers a balanced blend of daily comfort and performance. It comes with two keys, all original manuals, and a clean title in hand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
